'''Al-Sultan Abdullah I Sri Dhanmaru Aadheettha Mahaa Radhun''' ({{lang-dv|އައްސުލްޠާން ޢަބްދުﷲ އެއްވަނަ ސިރީ ދަންމަރު އާދީއްތަ މަހާރަދުން}}) was the [[Sultan]] of the [[Maldives]] from 1374 to 1376.

He was vizier to the court before forcing his wife Queen [[Khadijah of the Maldives|Khadijah]] to abdicate, and succeeding to the throne. In his third year of reign his wife killed him while he was asleep in bed and reclaimed the throne once again.

